'''[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]'''的签证政策是根据《菲律宾移民法》所制定的，该法由[[菲律宾外交部|菲律宾外交部]]和菲律宾移民局共同执行，但签证仅由菲律宾移民局签发<ref name=CA613>{{cite web|url=http://www.chanrobles.com/commonwealthactno613.htm|title=COMMONWEALTH ACT NO. 613|date=August 26, 1940|accessdate=2015-03-29|archive-date=2018-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181210113308/http://www.chanrobles.com/commonwealthactno613.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一般情况下，外籍人士在进入菲律宾前，需要到菲律宾驻各地使领馆办理签证后才能入境。以下人士可享有免签资格：
*[[东南亚国家联盟|东南亚国家联盟]]成员国公民
*其他具有免签资格的外国公民<ref>{{cite web|title=Compare visa requirements of countries in South East Asia|url=http://aroundtheworldinaday.com/philippines_thailand_comparison/thailand_visa_philippines_visa/|website=aroundtheworldinaday.com|accessdate=15 July 2014|archive-date=2014-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719092747/http://aroundtheworldinaday.com/philippines_thailand_comparison/thailand_visa_philippines_visa/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*[[海外菲律宾人|海外菲律宾人]]（若临时返回菲律宾，可适用此政策）

==签证类型==
根据《菲律宾移民法》，菲律宾签证可分为非移民签证（9(A)－9(G)）和移民签证（13－13(G)）<ref name=CA613/>。另外，菲律宾还设有特别类型的签证，分别是特别投资者居留签证<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boi.gov.ph/pdf/downlodableforms/incentives/sirv/SIRV%20FAQs.pdf|title=QUESTIONS & ANSWERS : Special Investors Resident Visa Program|date=November 14, 2007|publisher=Philippine Board of Investments|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120611205043/http://www.boi.gov.ph/pdf/downlodableforms/incentives/sirv/SIRV%20FAQs.pdf|archivedate=2012年6月11日}}</ref>、特别创造就业机会签证、特别退休人员签证<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pra.gov.ph/main/srrv_program?page=1|title=Special Resident Retiree's Visa|date=May 5, 2011|publisher=Philippine Retirement Authority|access-date=2012-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130122032343/http://www.pra.gov.ph/main/srrv_program?page=1|archive-date=2013-01-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和特别离岸金融工作签证<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.immigration.gov.ph/index.php/visa-requirements/special-visa/special-employment-visa-for-offshore-banking-unit|title=Special Employment Visa for Offshore Banking Unit|accessdate=February 24, 2014|publisher=菲律宾移民局|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228154721/http://www.immigration.gov.ph/index.php/visa-requirements/special-visa/special-employment-visa-for-offshore-banking-unit|archivedate=2014年2月28日}}</ref>。

==免签证==
[[Image:Visa_policy_of_the_Philippines.png|thumb]]
菲律宾的免签证政策，是根据[[菲律宾总统|菲律宾总统]][[卡洛斯·加西亚|卡洛斯·加西亚]]于1960年11月9日签署的《第408号行政令》所制定<ref>{{cite web|title=Executive Order No. 408, s. 1960|url=http://www.gov.ph/1960/11/09/executive-order-no-408-s-1960/|website=Official Gazette of the Republic of the Philippines|accessdate=1 November 2014|archive-date=2014-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101043120/http://www.gov.ph/1960/11/09/executive-order-no-408-s-1960/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。任何符合免签证资格的人士，可直接凭护照直接入境，无需办理签证，但护照有效期不得少于6个月<ref name=BIextends>{{cite web|url=http://immigration.gov.ph/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=171&Itemid=78|title=BI extends stay of foreign tourists|date=August 6, 2007|publisher=Philippine Bureau of Immigration|access-date=2015-03-29|archive-date=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313043823/http://immigration.gov.ph/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=171&Itemid=78|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=FAQ-General />。

符合免签证资格的人士，可每次向菲律宾移民局申请居留期限2个月，但不得超过2年<ref name=BIextends />。对于持签证入境的人士，可每次向菲律宾移民局申请居留期限1个月，但不得超过6个月，且出境时需要出境机票<ref name=FAQ-General>[http://www.immigration.gov.ph/index.php/component/content/article/10-faqs/33-general-information?showall=1&limitstart= Guidelines on Entry Visas of Temporary Visitors to the Philippines] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315143240/http://www.immigration.gov.ph/index.php/component/content/article/10-faqs/33-general-information?showall=1&limitstart= |date=2014-03-15 }}</ref>。

===政策变更===
2013年7月1日，菲律宾移民局宣布扩大外国人免签入境范围，并于同年8月开始执行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://globalnation.inquirer.net/81291/tourists-initial-stay-in-ph-extended-from-21-to-30-days|title=Tourists’ initial stay in PH extended from 21 to 30 days|date=July 24, 2013|publisher=Philippine Daily Inquirer|accessdate=2015-03-29|archive-date=2015-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150325000639/http://globalnation.inquirer.net/81291/tourists-initial-stay-in-ph-extended-from-21-to-30-days/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年3月，菲律宾计划向[[中华人民共和国|中国]]和[[印度|印度]]公民免签证<ref>[http://www.financialexpress.com/article/travel/latest-updates-travel/philippines-proposes-to-remove-entry-visa-requirements-for-india-and-china/52091/ Philippines proposes to remove entry visa requirements for India and China] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322042233/http://www.financialexpress.com/article/travel/latest-updates-travel/philippines-proposes-to-remove-entry-visa-requirements-for-india-and-china/52091/ |date=2015-03-22 }}</ref>。

